c: 18
v: 14
t: "wqwwayna qulubuhum bal'iyman, washadadna ezymthm bh, hin qamuu bayn yaday almalik alkafr, wahu ylwmhm ealaa tark eibadat al'asnam faqaluu lh: rabuna aladhi nebdh hu rabu alsmwat walard, ln naebud ghyrh min alalht, law qulna ghyr hdha lkunna qad qulna qawlana jayrana beydana ean alhq"